videos.description: The snap to punter Ron Coluzzi is too high, so he takes off and, with daylight in front of him, trips on his own feet to set Michigan up in prime field position.
videos.headline: Michigan gets big break on Iowa's botched punt

videos.description: Wilton Speight pass complete to Jehu Chesson for 29 yds to the Iowa 20 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: W. Speight pass,to J. Chesson for 29 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Ty Isaac takes the handoff and finds a hole before barreling through the defenders at the goal line to score boosting Michigan's lead to 10-0.
videos.headline: Michigan finds the end zone on Isaac's TD

videos.description: Michigan redecorates Iowa's visiting locker room with a Wolverine centered theme.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Must-See (Michigan gives Iowa locker room makeover) 2016/11/12 ESHEET 3PV

videos.headline: Michigan gives Iowa locker room makeover

videos.description: Having Michigan backed up to their own goal line, Iowa hits De'Veon Smith in the back field to score the safety for the Hawkeyes.
videos.headline: Defense gets Iowa on the board with a safety

videos.description: C.J. Beathard pass complete to Akrum Wadley for 26 yds to the Mich 25 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: C. Beathard pass,to A. Wadley for 26 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Facing 4th-and-goal from the three yardline, Iowa goes for it and it pays off when C.J. Beathard hits Akrum Wadley for the touchdown to cut Michigan's lead to 10-8.
videos.headline: Iowa's 4th down gamble pays off in TD

videos.description: Iowa head coach Kirk Ferentz talks about what the offense needs to do in the second half
videos.headline: Iowa head coach Kirk Ferentz talks about what the offense needs to do in the second half

videos.description: Ron Coluzzi kickoff for 45 yds , Khalid Hill return for 23 yds to the Mich 43 Khalid Hill fumbled, recovered by Iowa Brady Ross
videos.headline: R. Coluzzi kick for 45 yds,K. Hill return for 23 yds,K. Hill fumbled, recovered by Iowa B. Ross

videos.description: Kenny Allen drills a career-long 51-yard field goal to give Michigan the lead back at 13-11.
videos.headline: Michigan retakes the lead with 51-yard FG

videos.description: Wilton Speight pass intercepted Manny Rugamba return for no gain to the Iowa 25
videos.headline: Iowa's Manny Rugamba rips away a pass from a Michigan receiver for the interception

videos.description: C.J. Beathard pass intercepted Channing Stribling return for no gain to the Mich 16
videos.headline: C. Beathard pass intercepted,C. Stribling return  for 0 yds

videos.description: Iowa continues the day of upset by stunning Michigan on a last-second 33-yard field goal for a 14-13 win.
videos.headline: Iowa shocks Michigan on last-second FG

videos.description: After getting run off the field last week against Penn State, Kirk Ferentz is proud of how his team picked themselves up off the mat and pulled off the upset over Michigan.
videos.headline: Ferentz proud of team's bounce back for upset

videos.description: Iowa kicker Keith Duncan on his emotions before and after the game winning kick
videos.headline: Iowa kicker Keith Duncan on his emotions before and after the game winning kick

videos.description: Heather Dinich examines what could happen to Michigan in the College Football Playoff rankings after losing to Iowa.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Analysis (Michigan likely to drop behind Ohio State) 2016/11/12 SC

videos.headline: Michigan likely to drop behind Ohio State

videos.description: Iowa kicked a game-winning field goal to knock off Jim Harbaugh and Michigan.  The same scenario happened when they faced off in 1985 and Harbaugh was the Wolverines QB.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Iowa's win over Michigan is déjà vu to 1985) 2016/11/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Iowa's win over Michigan is déjà vu to 1985

videos.description: Jim Harbaugh gives credit to Iowa for beating Michigan and says the Wolverines have to move on after suffering their first loss of the season.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Presser (Harbaugh says Michigan has to move on and respond) 2016/11/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harbaugh says Michigan has to move on and respond
